            <history-note id="DLM72731"><amended-provision>Section 95(2)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>repealed</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>25 January 2005</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM331111">section 200</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Crown
